You can copy and paste the code below into an HTML file (e.g., `index.html`) and open it in a web browser that supports Web VR.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VR Egg Frying Chat with Building</title>
    <script src="https://aframe.io/releases/1.2.0/aframe.min.js"></script>
